quran[27]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,34,"Chisimu ŵakun'jogopa Allah akwete kupata kwa Ambuje ŵao Matimbe Gachindimba (Mbepo)."
  68,35,"Ana twatende Asilamu nti chisawu akuleeŵa (pakwalipila mwakulandana)?"
  68,36,"Chipali chichi kukwenu! Ana nkwiilanya chinauli?"
  69,31,"“Kaneka ni mumponye ku Moto Waukali.”"
  69,32,"“Kaneko muntaŵikanye m’malundelunde (ga unyolo), ulewu wakwe makono makumi nsano nagaŵili (70).”"
  69,33,"Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jukaakunkulupilila Allah Jwakuchimbichika nnope."
  70,25,"Lyakumpa nkuŵenda ni nkwimidwa jwakwe (ligongo lyakulisiŵilila kuŵenda)."
  70,26,"Ni aŵala ŵaakwitichisya ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo."
  70,27,"Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa nkuijogopa ilagasyo ya M’mbuje gwao."
  71,22,"“Ni atesile malindi gamakulungwa nnope.”"
  71,23,"“Soni aŵele ali nkuti: ‘Ngasinneka (galagatila) milungu jenu ata panandi, ngasinnogwa kwaleka Awadda, Asuwa'a, Ayagh'utha, Aya’uka ni Anasra.”"
  71,24,"“Soni ŵanganyao pamasile paŵasokonesye (ŵandu) ŵajinji, ni ngasimwajonjechesya ŵakulitenda lupuso (chine chakwe) ikaŵeje kupotelape.”"
  72,19,"Soni chisimu ndema ja jwajimi kapolo jwa Allah (Muhammadi ﷺ pa swala) achim'bombaga (Allah), ŵasigele panandi (achimajini) kuti ammate (ligongo lya winji nnope ni kunyambatikana pakusaka kupikanila Qur’an)."
  72,20,"Jilani: “Chisimu ngun'galagatila M'mbuje gwangu pe, ni ngangum'bwanganya Najo julijose.”"
  72,21,"Jilani: “Chisimu une nganingola kukwenu (machili gakumpela) isausyo kapena chongoko.”"
  73,13,"Ni yakulya yakwama (palukosi) kwisa soni ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  73,14,"Lisiku lya lichitenganyika litaka kwisa soni matumbi, ni gachiŵa matumbigo chisau liunjili lya nsanga wakupwelembwesuka."
  73,15,"Chisimu Uwwe tutumisye kukwenu Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) kuŵa mboni pa jenumanja, mpela yatwatite pakutumisya kwa Afiriauna Ntenga (Musa)."
  74,10,"Kwa achimakafili ngasiliŵa lyakwepepala."
  74,11,"Munekaani ni mundu jwanan'gumbile jikajikape."
  74,12,"Ninampele ipanje yejinji."
  75,7,"Sano ndema ja lichikolondoka liso (ligongo lya woga)."
  75,8,"Ni kutyoka kuŵala kwa mwesi."
  75,9,"Ni kusonganganyisyidwa lyuŵa ni mwesi."
  76,1,"Ana nganijipita kwamundu mbinga jelewu ja ndaŵi nkanaŵe kuŵa chindu chanti ni kusalidwa?"
  76,2,"Chisimu Uwwe tun'gumbile mundu kuumila mwindondwa lyakuwanganyichilana (lya mesi ga ŵalume ni ŵakongwe), kuti tun'dinje (ni malamusi Getu), ni tuntesile kuŵa jwakupikana, jwakulola."
  76,3,"Chisimu Uwwe tunsaalichiisye jwalakwejo litala (lyambone ni lyakusakala, sano ili ni nsyene) kuŵa jwakutogolela (pakusagula lyambonelyo) kapena kuŵa jwakanila (pakusagula lyakusakala)."